         <p style="white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 23.2727px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">记录法律路上的喜怒哀乐</p>
         <p style="white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 23.2727px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br /></p>
         <p style="white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 23.2727px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="line-height: 23.2727px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">点“</span><strong style="line-height: 23.2727px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 82, 255);">阅读原文</span></strong><span style="line-height: 23.2727px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">”看更多精彩</span><br /></p>
